show.title: Little Poor Thing Rises by Bearing Children, Reigns Over the Electronics Factory
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/sf2QxP
show.description: Exploited for her ability to bear children, a powerless young woman is treated as nothing more than a tool. But with razor-sharp wit and unbreakable resolve, she flips her fate and seizes an empire built on steel and circuits. This is a story where survival transforms into dominance, and a victim rises to rule her own world.
